Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耸立在米加罗城市的\N四粒陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些陨石拥有的真正意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们是还未知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石发着蓝色的光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这定会有什么事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:01:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在发光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享，你也看到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿、真儿!还活着吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了\N要联络城市警察才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:03:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55\fad(200,200)\pos(480,680)}从妖魔石中逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了叫我们到来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说有东西要让我们看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是美梦妮，这是我丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会这样吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道，一脸严肃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会有私生子也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家已到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么小孩子?艾莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个\N要给我们看的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在仓库，跟着来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这很厉害...\N-喜欢吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战斗用的‘猎犬号’
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是美梦妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去找恋人\N老是在埋头研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我没有丈夫和私生子\N放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂、喂，是城市警察吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友发生了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里\N我朋友真儿在这里被...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸进陨石中吗?无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你科幻电影看多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,署长，我在这里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在里面呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么想\N也没可能会被吸进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的\N如不快救真儿出来...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再捉弄大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没空去听小孩的胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-过来，送你回家\N-是真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真吵!\N-大家等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走...喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这妖魔石的守护者\N圣米迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到死心为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样挣扎，在这世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是逃不过我的掌心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!究竟怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼，怎么了?\N在吃惊什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这里是...\N看看外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了米加罗大厦的相反方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从陨石中移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这些陨石中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我为所欲为的世界\N明白了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想、想对我做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近妖魔石会认为没事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被陨石吸进后过了24小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你便会变成这陨石的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信不信是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样，只得一天的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何不相信我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话\N只好由我们去想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了什么事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有什么事\N明天在学校才说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因我要上课外活动\N要早点起床
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管这些，真儿他有麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎，真儿他?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?真儿在昨天失踪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:08:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此享、乱童和莫莉好像去找他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会默不作声的离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先到真儿的家看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能留下什么线索也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩，真儿那家伙\N竟要别人替他担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的时间会碰上交通堵塞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到公园绕道去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在早上也没有起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到他房间看了后\N竟是间空房
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么头绪吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个认真的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没有试过离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书包和教科书也没拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有离家出走的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了安全起见\N到屋顶和逃生梯调查下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真儿...\N-真儿...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是莫莉的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的话便回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里，大家，我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手开始水晶化...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救...救我出去呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我出去吧...救命啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像掉了道路雷电的车匙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能在真儿的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是图画的功课
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米加罗城市夜景的风景画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来\N为何那陨石是蓝色的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像跟事件有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，去调查陨石的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷电，去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我，我们不能不管真儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后交给我们吧\N我们会想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见真儿被吸进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发着蓝色的光\N从内伸出可怕的手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把真儿拉进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积克，你认为怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕只有发光时\N才能从内部进出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了，你们回学校去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊!\N就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想帮忙把同学救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送他们回学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去调查别的陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿，你要努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Borg Get On!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如把探测器调校至最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能调查里面的东西也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有半天\N我便会成为这陨石的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，谁来救我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，激光完全起不了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有等待下次发光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿所画的画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时钟的时间是9点5分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如被吸进去是之后的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余下的时间便没有太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是哪一粒陨石会发光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷电，你那边有异样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要冲进发光的那一粒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发光了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全的滑进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如没坐上钢铁战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体便会散开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿，你在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉斯好像进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能拖拖拉拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们只能等陨石发光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也办不到，可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉斯，拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从何处进来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔，出现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有威势的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不说，就将你们打成蜂窝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈，能做到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起收拾你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样?受到教训了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼现在怎样?给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有数十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他便会跟妖魔石一体化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道妖魔石秘密的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能让他活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你也变作妖魔石的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你们那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来保护真儿给你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻影...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎挣扎也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余下的时间只有很少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可受到迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿该在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师，艾莉斯老师...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿现在听到我的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在模糊的意识中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我的声音有反应，真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师已经来了，没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿，你要振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点逃离这里才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握出口的关键\N是刚才的妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，搏一搏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!竟伤害了妖魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受一下妖魔石的威力吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉斯怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:16:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如这样下去会被吸进异次元\N再也回来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了，给我传达吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射向发光的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射向发光的中心...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积克! 恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准了，开火!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉斯，成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，竟出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来作你的对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改造人力量被吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，离开那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积克，这家伙由我来\N别出手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:18:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?迷迪奥被打败了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，刚才他的波动断绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是超音战士所为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔石是不可让任何人接近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已说了很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但妖魔石有这么重要吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的什么都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比达你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妖魔石是令魔界\N复活的重要关键
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达士多捷特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在由你担任\N镇压米加罗城市的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可让超音战士知道\N妖魔石的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要使用魔力去令魔界复活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们则服从\N达士多捷特的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-去镇压城市\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿你醒了吗，已没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享已告诉了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是超音战士\N从陨石中把你救出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超音战士?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到是艾莉斯老师的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果艾莉斯是超音战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会是个超级英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-艾莉斯，是吧\N-是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真儿，振作点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包围着米加罗城市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满神秘力量的四粒妖魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会对我们有什么影响呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
